# Pricing transformation follows a 24-month path from diagnostic to embedded capability
@type: timeline

@step: Months 1–3 | Diagnostic and Design | Transaction analysis, segment willingness-to-pay, MAP enforcement
@step: Months 4–9 | Quick Win Deployment | Pocket price compliance, CRM guardrails, comp redesign
@step: Months 10–18 | Value-Based Repricing | Segment-by-segment list price rebuilds, price-to-value messaging
@step: Months 19–24 | Pricing Capability | Dedicated pricing team, analytics platform, continuous optimization

@source: BCG Pricing Transformation Methodology, 2024

@notes: Month 1–3 requires transaction data access and field cooperation. If either is blocked, the diagnostic is compromised. Escalate these as prerequisites to the C-suite immediately.

